From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: ImmortalWrt
Date: Fri, 18 Jul 2026 01:30:00 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] pmdomain: mediatek: allow AIROHA_CPU_PM_DOMAIN on ARCH_AIROHA

The AIROHA_CPU_PM_DOMAIN config is defined inside the "MediaTek PM Domains"
menu which depends on ARCH_MEDIATEK || COMPILE_TEST. This prevents the
option from being visible on ARCH_AIROHA platforms, causing cpufreq to
fail with "Failed to set OPP config" because the CPU power domain driver
is not built.

Add ARCH_AIROHA to the menu dependency so that AIROHA_CPU_PM_DOMAIN can
be enabled on Airoha platforms without enabling COMPILE_TEST.

Signed-off-by: ImmortalWrt
---
 drivers/pmdomain/mediatek/Kconfig | 2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

--- a/drivers/pmdomain/mediatek/Kconfig
+++ b/drivers/pmdomain/mediatek/Kconfig
@@ -1,6 +1,6 @@
 # SPDX-License-Identifier: GPL-2.0-only

 menu "MediaTek PM Domains"
-	depends on ARCH_MEDIATEK || COMPILE_TEST
+	depends on ARCH_MEDIATEK || ARCH_AIROHA || COMPILE_TEST

 config MTK_SCPSYS
 	bool "MediaTek SCPSYS Support"
